  "recipeInstructions": "1. Layer the sliced vegetables in a large casserole dish in the order specified.\n2. Mix together the sauce ingredients and pour over the vegetables.\n3. Cook for six hours at high temperature or 12 hours at low temperature.\n(Serves: 8)",
